        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>Netherlandish Renaissance-Baroque ceramics styles [300106356], Netherlandish Renaissance-Baroque styles [300021051], Renaissance-Baroque regional styles [300112572], Renaissance-Baroque styles [300021033], Renaissance-Baroque styles and periods [300021031], European [300020656], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
